    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in running order. It requires substantial mechanical attention, specifically a complete engine overhaul and likely a new transmission, as the current systems are non-functional. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior will need a deep clean and some upholstery repair. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor.",
